1. *Zaustavite* se na crvenom semaforu. (Stop at the red traffic light.)
2. Oni su *zaustavili* automobil. (They stopped the car.)
3. Ona nas je *zaustavila* da joj pokažemo put. (She stopped us to show her the way.)
4. Policija je *zaustavila* automobil. (The police stopped the car.)
5. *Zaustavila* sam da vidim šta se dešava. (I stopped to see what was happening.)
6. *Zaustavite* se i pošaljite poruku. (Stop and send a message.)